09:48.120 --> 09:51.040
Yes. He wanted to stay here.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.680
At busy times, he'd often sleep over.

09:53.720 --> 09:56.920
He couldn't wait to plan the menu,

09:53.720 --> 09:56.920
