10:01.360 --> 10:02.720
No, not all night, no.

10:02.760 --> 10:04.680
But certainly well into the night.

10:05.240 --> 10:06.920
He was a total workaholic.

10:07.480 --> 10:11.160
And who else did he know on the island?

10:07.480 --> 10:11.160
Suppliers, decorators?

10:11.200 --> 10:13.240
No, no one.

10:13.520 --> 10:16.560
Dexter deals with supplies and I deal with everyone else.

10:16.760 --> 10:19.960
-Well,

10:16.760 --> 10:19.960
