10:43.240 --> 10:45.200
Man was a genius.

10:45.240 --> 10:47.360
Just complete and utter dedication to the kitchen.

10:47.960 --> 10:51.440
And during evening service, was there anything unusual,

10:47.960 --> 10:51.440
anything untoward?

10:51.480 --> 10:53.000
It was seamless.

10:53.240 --> 10:55.760
And you all left together at 11:30,

10:53.240 --> 10:55.760
went directly to the villa,

10:55.800 --> 10:57.960
