11:39.120 --> 11:41.960
the CCTV here, teething problems?

11:42.240 --> 11:46.760
Yes, it was a complicated system

11:42.240 --> 11:46.760
to set up.

11:47.160 --> 11:50.840
Robert wanted it everywhere. He liked to be

11:47.160 --> 11:50.840
on top of things.

11:52.240 --> 11:55.840
I just wish we...

11:57.840 --> 12:00.680
